These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: car, skateboard, tram, ship, boat, train
6 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, guinea-pig, hedgehog, mouse, rabbit
 1. the person driving the tram is in an odd position##4
 2. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
 3. the person driving the boat is not the owner of the mouse##6
 4. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
 5. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 7. the owner of the mouse is not the person driving the skateboard##6
 8. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
 9. the person driving the car is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the person driving the ship##7
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
11. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
12. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
13. the owner of the cat is the person driving the car##1
14. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
15. the person driving the train is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Transport   | ship   | car | tram   | train     | skateboard    | boat   |
| Pet           | mouse | cat   | rabbit | hedgehog | guinea-pig | goldfish |

