.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, prince, bolivar, vegafina, siglo, dunhill
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, lacrosse, parkour, surfing, swimming
 1. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
 2. the bongani-smoker is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5
 4. the person who's sport is basketball is not the vegafina-smoker##6
 5. the bongani-smoker is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 8. the siglo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the dunhill-smoker##5
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3
10. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the siglo-smoker and the prince-smoker##7
11. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
13. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5
14. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Cigar   | siglo        | vegafina | dunhill    | bongani    | bolivar | prince |
| Sport      | basketball | surfing  | swimming | parkour | baseball | lacrosse      |

