.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-4::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: skydiving, card-games, photography, sudoku, collecting, video-games
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: crime, drama, fantasy, horror, superhero, western
 1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 2. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
 3. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 5. the person watching drama movies is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6
 6. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is collecting##7
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is video-games##7
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 9. the person watching crime movies is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is sudoku##7
10. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
12. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
13. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
14. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3   |       4       |    5    |   6   |
| Hobby      | sudoku | card-games | video-games | photography | collecting | skydiving   |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | horror      | crime | superhero     | western | drama |

