.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, classical, electronic, gospel, pop, punk
There are 6 different favourite colors: green, black, brown, emerald, light-blue, aquamarine
 1. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the right of the fan of punk##5
 2. the person who likes green is somewhere to the right of the person who likes emerald##5
 3. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 4. the fan of blues is on the far left##1
 5. the fan of pop is between the person who likes light-blue and the fan of punk##2
 6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the fan of punk is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
 8. the fan of punk is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the fan of blues##7
 9. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
10. the person who likes green is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes light-blue is the fan of classical##1
12. the person who likes brown is not the fan of classical##6
13. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
14. the person who likes brown is the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |  3   |     4     |     5      |   6    |
| Music-Genre   | blues | punk | pop  | classical | electronic | gospel |
| Color           | aquamarine  | black  | emerald | light-blue  | brown     | green    |

