 8. the modern house is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
 9. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4
10. the ranch-style house is in an odd position##4
11. the art-deco house is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
12. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the car##1
13. the modern house is on the left or right of the palace house##3
14. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the modern house and the art-deco house##7

.:: Answer ::.
