.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-19::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: climbing, rowing, volleyball, skateboarding, weightlifting, rugby
The people use 6 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, skateboard, train, tram, trike
 1. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 2. the person who's sport is climbing is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
 5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person driving the boat##2
 7. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
 8. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
 9. the person who's sport is rowing is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
11. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
12. the person driving the tram is somewhere between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person driving the motorbike##7
13. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Sport         | rowing   | weightlifting | climbing      | skateboarding | rugby  | volleyball   |
| Transport   | train | trike  | motorbike | boat   | tram | skateboard |

