.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: tulip, lily, sunflower, orchid, marigold, balloon-flower
The people have 6 different jobs:  accountant, dressmaker, fisherman, journalist, project-manager, scientist
 1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
 2. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 3. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the right of the fisherman##5
 4. the person who growstulip is somewhere between the journalist and the dressmaker##7
 5. the scientist is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
 6. the person who growssunflower is the project-manager##1
 7. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
 8. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the person who growstulip##5
 9. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5
10. the dressmaker is somewhere to the right of the scientist##5
11. the scientist is on the right of the fisherman##1
12. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
13. the person who growslily is somewhere between the person who growstulip and the person who growssunflower##7
14. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
15. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the person who growsmarigold##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Flower   | sunflower         | orchid | lily | tulip   | balloon-flower | marigold  |
| Job     | project-manager | journalist  | fisherman  | scientist | dressmaker  | accountant |

 